Class Climber

  • java.lang.Object
    • Climber

  • public class Climber
extends java.lang.Object
    The Climber class stores information about individual climbers including: name, age, gender and a list of mountains they have climbed.
    Version:
    1.0 (08/11/2017)
    Author:
    (Michael Westerby)
